Aas Paas Episode 08 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 9th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

snippet.title: SIDEMEN CHARITY MATCH 2025 [OFFICIAL STREAM]
snippet.description:
Sidemen Charity Match 2025

Donate here: https://www.sidemenfc.com 

On the 8th of March Sidemen FC and YouTube Allstars are coming together to play the 2025 Charity Match at Wembley Stadium.

Use the hashtag #SDMNCharityMatch to talk about the game!

OFFICIAL STREAM starts at 2:10pm GMT

Kick off time is at 3pm GMT

The Sidemen Charity Match 2025 is in aid of the following charities and funds raised will be split as follows:

Bright Side 43%
BBC Children in Need 50%
M7 Education 7%

We will also donate all of the profit we make through the match and related activities to the following charities:

Bright Side 86%
M7 Education 14%

Any donations you make are greatly appreciated and going to great causes! We hope you enjoy the match.

For full details and terms and conditions please visit https://sidemenfc.com.

Viewers of this livestream are strictly prohibited from re-streaming or rebroadcasting this content on any platform. Any unauthorised re-streaming will result in the immediate removal of the infringing livestream and a copyright strike issued to the violator.

snippet.title: Aakash Gupta | Angry Young Man | Full Stand-up Comedy Special
snippet.description:
UK & USA TOUR 2025 Tickets Link : https://linktr.ee/theskygupta | Buy tickets & watch me perform live in your city :)

This is my full special which was released on insider in Dec 2023 on a pay per view basis. Thank you to everyone who bought tickets for the special then. It was my first time experimenting with the business model of releasing a comedy special online & your support helped us in producing this with our own money. Now after almost 2 years of shooting this I am releasing the whole show on Youtube for everyone to watch & enjoy. Hope you all like it :)

‚ÄúAngry Young Man‚Äù is Aakash Gupta‚Äôs first hour-long standup comedy special. Frustrated and grumpy about things he sees and feels, the comedian who is always asked, ‚ÄúTu hasta kyu nahi?‚Äù expresses his annoyance through humorous stories about life, from school days, to his recent trip to Europe. Some of you may have seen this show live in your city and now you can watch it again, online with your friends and loved ones. If you have not watched him before, don't worry, here is your chance to experience this hilarious show in HD.

With his agitated and ranting style of comic delivery, brace yourself as you laugh your socks off at the ‚ÄúAngry Young Man‚Äù. 

UK Tour March 2025 Tickets : https://linktr.ee/aakashgupta2024uk
US TOUR Apr May 2025 Tickets : https://theticketworld.com/AG

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Saved In Drafts | Episode 3 - New Beginning | Mini Series | Take A Break Originals
snippet.description:
Amit finally gathers the courage to express what his heart has been holding onto for so long. With a plan in place and hope in his eyes, he is ready to take the leap. But just as he prepares to confess, Darshana stands at a crossroads‚Äîready to embrace a new beginning in Pune.
Will their story find its way to love, or will it remain‚Ä¶ saved in drafts?

snippet.description:
Bapuji ki Jidd | Tapu ki Shadi | Gokuldham Society | Sonu ki shadi

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

snippet.title: Phulera Ka Panchayati Raj | Asli Pradhan Kaun? ft. Neena Gupta, Faisal Malik, Chandan Roy
snippet.description:
Manju Devi ke haathon aayi hai badi zimmedaari, Phulera vaasiyon ki shikayatein durr karne ki hai baari! Dekhiye kaise Manju Devi apni soojh-boojh dikhayengi, har samasya ka hal nikalke 'Women Empowerment' ka message de jaayengi!

#TVF #Phulera #PanchayatiRaj 

The Ministry of Panchayati Raj (MoPR), Government of India, is responsible for overseeing all matters related to Panchayati Raj and Panchayati Raj Institutions (PRIs) across the country. MoPR plays a pivotal role in promoting the decentralization process and strengthening rural local governance in States and Union Territories. For more information, visit the Ministry's official website: https://panchayat.gov.in

This film highlights the Ministry of Panchayati Raj‚Äôs initiative to transform women‚Äôs representation and roles in Panchayati Raj Institutions by eliminating proxy participation. It aims to create widespread awareness about capable and empowered Women Leadership in Panchayats (‡§™‡§Ç‡§ö‡§æ‡§Ø‡§§‡•ã‡§Ç ‡§Æ‡•á‡§Ç ‡§∏‡§Æ‡§∞‡•ç‡§• ‡§è‡§µ‡§Ç ‡§∏‡§∂‡§ï‡•ç‡§§ ‡§Æ‡§π‡§ø‡§≤‡§æ ‡§®‡•á‡§§‡•É‡§§‡•ç‡§µ), women empowerment, and women-led development in rural areas.

Let‚Äôs champion true leadership and say no to Pradhan Pati or Sarpanch Pati wherever it prevails!

The Ministry of Panchayati Raj (MoPR), Government of India, is responsible for overseeing all matters related to Panchayati Raj and Panchayati Raj Institutions (PRIs) across the country. MoPR plays a pivotal role in promoting the decentralization process and strengthening rural local governance in States and Union Territories. For more information, visit the Ministry's official website: https://panchayat.gov.in

This film highlights the Ministry of Panchayati Raj‚Äôs initiative to transform women‚Äôs representation and roles in Panchayati Raj Institutions by eliminating proxy participation. It aims to create widespread awareness about capable and empowered Women Leadership in Panchayats (‡§™‡§Ç‡§ö‡§æ‡§Ø‡§§‡•ã‡§Ç ‡§Æ‡•á‡§Ç ‡§∏‡§Æ‡§∞‡•ç‡§• ‡§è‡§µ‡§Ç ‡§∏‡§∂‡§ï‡•ç‡§§ ‡§Æ‡§π‡§ø‡§≤‡§æ ‡§®‡•á‡§§‡•É‡§§‡•ç‡§µ), women empowerment, and women-led development in rural areas.

Let‚Äôs champion true leadership and say no to Pradhan Pati or Sarpanch Pati wherever it prevails!
